snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online - E3 2017 Trailer
snippet.description:
Join over 10 million players worldwide in the game that keeps getting bigger.With hundreds of hours of base-game content, five released DLC game packs, the new Morrowind Chapter, and upcoming Horns of the Reach and Clockwork City DLC game packs, there’s never been a better time to discover The Elder Scrolls Online. Learn more at https://beth.games/2r3FFfF

Experience ESO: Morrowind, out now for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC/Mac.

To learn more about The Elder Scrolls Online, visit these sites:

Official Site: https://www.elderscrollsonline.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ElderScrollsOnline
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline
Instagram: https://instagram.com/elderscrollsonline
Google+: https://plus.google.com/+ElderScrollsOnline

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence. Online interactions not rated by the ESRB.
